overview:
Dollar3.com is a marketplace where you can outsource jobs for $3, $6, $9, $12 or $15. Ranging from small companies to corporate giants, almost all of them prefer to work with freelancers who work from home. Thanks to the Internet, more companies are finding they can outsource their jobs to home-based workers. Students can work on campus. Homemakers can work at home. Be your own boss. Work at your convenient hours.

Dollar3.com is the place where you find the best freelancers who are trustworthy, honest and hard-working. If you are jobless, tired of being a Jug head, want to fulfill your extra expenditures or want to have marvelous and tension free parties with friends: then signup at Dollar3.com. Registration is free.

Basically, Dollar3.com is a marketplace that links Buyers ( Small Businesses / Companies ) and Sellers ( Freelancers ). Sellers are freelancers who will complete a task or service for people (Buyers) willing to pay $3, $6, $9, $12 or $15. The price is fixed and the service, called a work/gig, could be : submitting your site to over 10000 different search engines and get you 10000 Backlinks, creating a company logo, advertising video for your website, invitation of their FaceBook fans to your sites and so on. The Sellers post their work / gigs at Dollar3.com. If you are interested, pay them $3, $6, $9, $12 or $15 using your PayPal account and provide your details/requirements. The Sellers will complete the work/gig for you.

Make extra money for your family by registering at Dollar3.com free, now. Post the work / gigs you are willing to do for $3, $6, $9, $12 or $15 and people who are interested will contact you directly at Dollar3.com.
